text: Rachelle Booth (born 31 August 1995) is an English taekwondo athlete. In May 2015, Booth competed in the -62kg category in the 2015 World Taekwondo Championships. She made the semi-finals, winning a bronze medal after losing to Mexican, Marta Calvo Gomez. The games were her debut World Championships and came only 18 months after joining the GB taekwondo team. ==References== Category:Living people Category:English female taekwondo practitioners Category:Sportspeople from Wigan Category:1995 births Category:World Taekwondo Championships medalists
